范闲，此剧主要讲述的是范闲从出生到成长的故事，算得上古装权谋剧中的经典之作。《庆余年》虽然是一部架空历史的古装剧 《琅琊榜》也是），但仍向我们展现了古时朝代人物的权谋，为了权利可以放弃亲情，放弃人性，此剧热度仍然在攀升！《琅琊榜》和《庆余年》两部剧都是古装权谋剧的经典之作，但比较起来，《琅琊榜》显得更为严肃，剧情的逻辑更为严谨，代入感更强！我个人认为，五年以内没有一部权谋剧可以超过《琅琊榜》。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9ac44546d8d66e5d77bdf955f35b0625_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/500352066"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxJjd0rzZgJhOEAMaCDczNDcwNjk5IOyM44wGMAA4+AFAGnIJNTAwMzUyMDY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1717811616.530305", "card_id": "Q_654901298", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 159}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "交易中有哪些第一性原理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有哪些近乎真理，不能忽略掉的定律？如果只留一条原则，你会留什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-aeeb4e74558e30f4adb05a1bb2dc90a5_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654901298"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIxJjd0rzZgJhOEAMaCTEwNzgxMTI4OSDP2NSxBjAAOPEEQBtyCTY1NDkwMTI5OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1717811616.530666", "card_id": "Q_658271056", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 126}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 6 月 7 日的《崩坏：星穹铁道》2.3 版本「再见，匹诺康尼」前瞻特别节目？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "还有就是叽米你为什么在游泳池里？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-3962b28d174880e23dbf7fb408f621fa_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658271056"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIxJjd